{"word":"H8156 - שָׁסַע - shâçaʻ - shaw-sah' - Cleave","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁסַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâçaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-sah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cleave"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரிந்திரு, பிள, விரி, கிழித்துப்போடு, அறு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to divide, to cleave, to part, to split"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) cleaving, to cleft (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to tear in two, to cleave in two"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>split</i> or <i>tear</i>; figuratively to <i>upbraid: - </i>cleave, (be) cloven ([footed]), rend, stay."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8156 - שָׁסַע - shâçaʻ - shaw-sah'/8156\">H8156</a>, <a href=\"#/H8157 - שֶׁסַע - sheçaʻ - sheh'-sah/8157\">H8157</a>"}]}